87ONPoEs9dE.description:
Trex sets the standard in "green" outdoor living and eco-friendly decking products. We're committed to creating a cleaner environemtn and a healthier future for our consumers and communities.  Our environmentally-friendly production practices recycle over 1.5 billion plastic bags that are then turned into beautiful and durable Trex decking.  Starting in 1992, long before the term "green" was even on the scene, our compostie technology was use to recycle plastic waste.  Today, the Trex brand has expanded to include a vareity of eco-friendly outdoor living product -- from decking and railing to deck lighting and outdoor furniture. Our outdoor living products offer more design flexibility and lower maintenance requirements than wood, as well as an environmentally responsible choice.
To learn how you can go green with our products -- or start your own local recycling program - visit www.trex.com/why-trex/eco-friendly-decking

_9eTY8Kxjt8.title: SHOT PUT Jacko GILL 24,35m WYR-24,03m-24,02m at World youth 2011 Lille.m4v
_9eTY8Kxjt8.description: In spite of a painful hand injury , Jacko GILL nearly achieved all his 3 goals at these World Youth Championships in Villeneuve d'Asq (France) . The most easy was to become World champion again , adding the youth title to his junior title last year (a fact only achieved by Usain Bolt in the men's events) . The second was to break the world youth shot put record during these champs and he did it at his 2nd attempt with a 24,35m performance and had two other attempts over the previous record and 24m . The third was to become the 1st shot putter of all ages groups , to throw officially over 25m in an official competition and it would certainly have been very close to that if it would not have been for this hand problem . Anyways he was one of the stars of these championships and as far as we can remember , we had never seen before a whole stadium standing up , clapping hands and cheering for a shot putter. Jacko was 4m exactly ahead of the silver medallist , a huge gap which could be compared to 20m over 100m , 300m on 1500m or 1m in the pole vault !  People had the feeling that all the other throwers were going slow motion compared to the New Zealander ....and indeed they were !  More than ever it demonstrates that high level shot put is a SPEED EVENT , not a STRENGTH EVENT !!! DP

uNQM3YC05E4.title: North Sea Giant.mp4
uNQM3YC05E4.description:
The 'Offshore Support Vessel of the Year Award' for 2012 was won by North Sea Shipping's 'North Sea Giant', built to DNV class at the Metalships & Docks shipyard in Vigo, Spain.
 
The North Sea Giant is considered to be the largest offshore vessel of this type ever built, with an overall length of 156m, beam of 30m and installed power of more than 22MW.
 
The vessel was given the prize for her innovative features, which include advanced dynamic positioning (DP) capability for DP operations based on a high redundancy level and high propulsion power.
 
North Sea Giant has a capacity for 120 people and its structure is highlighted by its heliport on the bow and a bridge placed up on the sixth deck of the vessel. The vessel boasts a working deck area of close to 3000 sqm.
 
Introduced in 2010, the 'Offshore Support Journal Awards' have been well received by the industry and this award recognizes the owner, designer and builder of an offshore support vessel that has been delivered in the past calendar year and is considered to have set an industry benchmark through innovative design and efficient operation.

Ic8kGfA0WVQ.description:
diagnostic auto multimarque Creader VII dispo sur http://www.materiel-hi-tech.fr
LAUNCH CREADER VII, est spécifiquement conçu pour les propriétaires de véhicule ou les professionnels de la mécanique afin de diagnostiquer une anomalie.

Ce n'est pas seulement un lecteur de codes OBDII/CAN, mais il permet aussi d'obtenir des données LIVE et de faire plusieurs tests et surtout il se demarque de tout ses concurrents par sa polyvalence, en effet cette merveille de technologie dernier né de la gamme Launch est desormais capable de diagnostiquer en plus du moteur ABS, SRS etc....

Ce lecteur supporte 4 languages dont le Français les diagnostiques sont en cours de traduction et deployer automatiquement lors des mises à jour internet à venir. Il est aussi possible d'updater ce lecteur via internet afin qu'il puisse faire scanner de nouveaux modèles de voiture ou d'ajouter des fonctions dans le futur.

Creader VII CERTIFIE 100% ORIGINAL LAUNCH  

Outil universel pour toutes marques de voiture certifiée OBDII , ceci inclut tous les véhicules Américains, Asiatiques et Européens (voiture ou camionnette)

 Cette outil d'analyse est multimarque mais vous permettra pour une marque en particulier de faire des analyses plus poussé ABS, SRS, AIRBAG etc... 

Pour ce faire il suffit de selectionner la marque du véhicule via le portail de mise à jour launch est l'implémenter définitivement dans le creader VII 

Nouvelles fonctionnalités:
 
Système de diagnostic complet du véhicule individuel
Aide mémoire Lieu DLC
Bibliothèque Recherche de code
Abréviations Lookup
Alarme buzzer
Batterie d'alimentation autonome
Mises à jour gratuites sur Internet (USB ou carte SD)
